[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0007","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0943","title":"Joomla! JA Showcase 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JA Showcase (com_jashowcase) 组件存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 index.php 的 jashowcase 动作中 controller 参数传递 `..`（点点）序列，绕过路径限制，读取服务器上任意敏感文件。该漏洞源于程序对用户输入的路径参数缺乏充分的过滤与校验，属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类漏洞，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。受影响版本为 Joomla! 使用 com_jashowcase 组件的相关部署。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0943"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-08T15:30:00.777","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:11.003","remediation":"该组件发布于 2010 年且已停止维护，不存在官方补丁。建议立即从 Joomla 后台卸载 com_jashowcase 组件，改用其他仍在维护的 Joomla 展示类扩展（如 RSMediaGallery）替代。如无法立即卸载，可在网站根目录 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteRule 拦截 controller 参数中包含 ../ 的请求，或通过 WAF 规则过滤 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlajashowcase-traversal.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/33486","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11090","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37692","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/55512","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11090","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0943.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0943.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0943.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-0943.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-0943-1516.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-0943.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-0943_18.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/Vulnerability-Templates/template2/cve-2010-0943-1517.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/13/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/2010/CVE-2010-0943.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0006","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0942","title":"Joomla! com_jvideodirect 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 内容管理系统中的 jVideoDirect 组件（com_jvideodirect）存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 文件的 controller 参数传递包含 ../ 序列的恶意路径，绕过目录访问限制，读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 网站，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，可能导致数据库配置、系统文件等敏感信息泄露，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0942"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-08T15:30:00.747","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:10.897","remediation":"该组件（com_jvideodirect）已长期无人维护，官方未发布安全补丁。建议立即在 Joomla 后台卸载该扩展；如因业务依赖无法卸载，需在控制器入口处对 controller 参数过滤 ../ 和空字节等目录遍历字符，同时可通过 Web 服务器规则（如 Apache mod_rewrite）拦截包含连续点号的查询字符串作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlajvideodirect-traversal.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11089","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37694","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/55513","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11089","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0942.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0942-1508.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0942-1509.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0942-1511.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-0942.yaml","https://github.com/SleepingBag945/dddd/blob/4c428a7c171275bfbb5fa72c2fb4bd7b48f4ff4a/common/config/pocs/CVE-2010-0942.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0005","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0759","title":"Core Design Joomla! Scriptegrator 插件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Core Design Scriptegrator 插件 1.4.1 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞。该漏洞位于 plugins/system/cdscriptegrator/libraries/highslide/js/jsloader.php 文件中，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 files[] 参数传入包含目录遍历序列（如 ../）的特制请求，实现任意文件读取。在特定配置下，该漏洞可被进一步利用为文件包含导致任意代码执行。此漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0759"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-02-27T00:30:00.883","updated":"2026-06-16T23:16:47.643","remediation":"立即升级 Core Design Scriptegrator 插件至最新版本（如已停止维护则彻底卸载该插件）。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器层面（如 .htaccess 或 Nginx 配置）对 plugins/system/cdscriptegrator/ 目录限制访问，并过滤 files[] 参数中的目录遍历序列（如 ../），仅允许白名单内的合法文件路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1002-exploits/joomlascriptegrator-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/38637","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11498","http://www.osvdb.org/62486","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38296","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/56380","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0759.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0005.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0004","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0696","title":"JoomlaWorks AllVideos Joomla 插件目录遍历漏洞","description":"JoomlaWorks 开发的 Joomla! 组件 AllVideos (Jw_allVideos) 3.0 至 3.2 版本中的 includes/download.php 存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 file 参数传递经过特殊构造的 `./../.../` 序列绕过路径限制，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞允许未授权攻击者读取服务器上任意敏感文件（如配置文件、数据库凭据等），危害较大。CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中危漏洞，建议用户立即升级或停用受影响组件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0696"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-02-23T18:30:00.717","updated":"2026-06-16T23:16:40.280","remediation":"升级 JoomlaWorks AllVideos 插件至 3.3 及以上版本，或在 Joomla 后台卸载该插件并更换为官方维护的替代插件。若无升级条件，可删除 `includes/download.php` 文件中的 `file` 参数处理逻辑，或在 Web 服务器层（如 .htaccess）限制 `download.php` 的直接访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/62331","http://secunia.com/advisories/38587","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11447","http://www.joomlaworks.gr/content/view/77/34/","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11447","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0696.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0696-1497.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0696-1498.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0696-1501.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0696-1500.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-0696.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0003","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0467","title":"Joomla! ccNewsletter 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 ccNewsletter 组件（com_ccnewsletter）1.0.5 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 发送特制请求，在 controller 参数中使用 ../ 路径回溯序列绕过目录限制，读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 网站，攻击者无需身份验证即可远程利用，可能导致数据库配置等敏感信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.8，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0467"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-02-02T17:30:00.407","updated":"2026-06-16T23:16:14.110","remediation":"厂商已于 2010 年发布 ccNewsletter 1.0.6 安全更新修复此漏洞，建议立即将组件升级至 1.0.6 或更高版本；如无法升级，应卸载或禁用该组件，同时通过 .htaccess 规则过滤 controller 参数中的 `..` 目录遍历序列作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":[