,"title":"Joomla! com_biblestudy 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Bible Study (com_biblestudy) 组件 6.1 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 index.php 的 studieslist 操作中向 controller 参数注入 .. (点点) 路径遍历序列，包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞属于本地文件包含 (LFI) 类型，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5 (HIGH)，影响使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点。攻击者可读取敏感系统文件 (如 /etc/passwd)、配置文件或包含恶意脚本实现代码执行。厂商已停止维护该组件，建议迁移至替代组件或升级至安全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0157"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-01-06T22:00:12.450","updated":"2026-06-16T23:15:35.200","remediation":"立即卸载 com_biblestudy 组件（版本 6.1 及以下均受影响）。如业务必须使用，请升级到已修复此目录遍历漏洞的最新版本；若开发者已不再维护，则彻底移除该组件。作为临时缓解措施，可在 Web 服务器或 WAF 层面拦截 URL 中 controller 参数包含 \"../\" 的请求，或编辑 Joomla 配置文件加入 `$controller = preg_replace('/[^A-Za-z0-9]/', '', $controller);` 进行输入过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlabiblestudy-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/37896","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37583","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10943","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0157.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0157-1486.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e61be9425da7cd98fab7bf6d914282e65c9f9042/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-0157.json","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2010-0157-1485.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-0157_21.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-0157.rules","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Apr/02/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/0ahmad0makki0/MyNuclei.V1.0/blob/38542bcf3aeb106084ec17df3981ddf081c73710/Public/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0157.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0107","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4231","title":"Camtron CMNC-200 IP 摄像机 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Camtron CMNC-200 全高清网络摄像机及 TecVoz CMNC-200 百万像素网络摄像机（固件版本 1.102A-008）的 Web 管理界面存在目录遍历漏洞。其 HTTP 服务在处理请求 URI 时未对 ../ 路径序列进行充分过滤与规范化校验，导致路径穿越防护失效。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向设备 80 端口发送包含 ../ 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，即可绕过目录限制读取设备文件系统上的任意文件，如配置文件、用户凭据等敏感信息。攻击仅需网络可达目标且无需登录凭证，影响上述固件版本的设备，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4231"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-11-17","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"由于厂商未发布正式补丁，建议在网络边界通过 ACL 限制仅授权管理 IP 访问摄像头 Web 管理端口（80/443），并使用 VLAN 隔离防止横向访问；如必须暴露 Web 界面，请在反向代理上启用 WAF 规则拦截包含 ../ 等目录遍历载荷的请求，并定期审计设备配置文件访问日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15505","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/514753/100/0/threaded","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4231.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4231.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4231.json","https://github.com/K3ysTr0K3R/CVE-2010-4231-EXPLOIT"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0106","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2861","title":"Adobe ColdFusion 管理员控制台目录遍历漏洞","description":"Adobe ColdFusion 9.0.1 及更早版本的管理员控制台（位于 /CFIDE/administrator/ 下多个页面）在处理 locale 参数时存在多个目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可在未认证的情况下，通过向 mappings.cfm、logging/settings.cfm、datasources/index.cfm、j2eepackaging/editarchive.cfm 及 enter.cfm 等页面的 locale 参数注入包含 ../ 的恶意路径，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件，进而可能获取配置文件、密码等敏感信息，造成信息泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2861"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-08-11","updated":"2010-08-11","remediation":"升级到 Adobe 已修复的 ColdFusion 版本：ColdFusion 9.0.1 应用 APSB10-18 安全更新，ColdFusion 9.0/8.x 升级至对应补丁版本；同时限制对 /CFIDE/administrator/ 目录的访问，并对 locale 参数做路径规范化校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T19:33:34.451687758+00:00","references":["https://www.adobe.com/support/security/bulletins/apsb10-18.html","https://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/coldfusion-directory-traversal-faq-cve-2010-2861/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2010-2861"],"poc_urls":["https://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/coldfusion-directory-traversal-faq-cve-2010-2861/"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0100","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2857","title":"Joomla! Music Manager 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Music Manager 组件存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 album.html 页面时未对 cid 参数进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可通过在 cid 参数中注入 \"../\"（点点点）目录遍历序列，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码哈希等敏感数据），并可能借此造成其他未明确的危害。该漏洞影响使用存在缺陷的 Music Manager 组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下即可通过构造特制请求远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分为 6.8，危害等级为中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2857"],"sources":["nuclei","exploit-db","cve"],"published":"2010-07-24","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用存在漏洞的 Joomla! Music Manager 第三方组件；若必须继续使用，请在组件 album.html 中对 cid 参数使用 intval() 强制取整并过滤 \"../\" 等路径穿越字符，同时升级到官方已修复该缺陷的版本。临时缓解措施包括在 Joomla 全局配置中将 PHP 的 allow_url_include 设为 Off，并将组件目录文件权限设为只读。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1007-exploits/joomlamusicmanager-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14274","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41485","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/60195","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2857.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0097","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2507","title":"Joomla! Picasa2Gallery 组件本地文件包含漏洞（LFI）","description":"Picasa2Gallery（com_picasa2gallery）组件 1.2.8 及更早版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传入包含 ../ 的路径序列，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd），并可能包含并执行本地文件造成进一步影响。攻击仅需构造特制 HTTP 请求，无需认证，利用条件为开启该组件且 PHP 未有效禁用空字节截断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2507"],"sources":["nuclei","cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2010-06-28","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"升级 Picasa2Gallery 组件到官方修复版本，或在 index.php 入口过滤 controller 参数中的 ../ 及空字节（%00），并配置 Joomla! 全局输入过滤以阻止目录遍历。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T18:42:14.489321313+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-2507","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981","http://secunia.com/advisories/40297","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41031","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59669","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlapicasa2gallery-lfi.txt"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlapicasa2gallery-lfi.txt"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/13981"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0094","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2128","title":"Joomla! JE Quotation Form 组件 目录遍历本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JE Quotation Form（com_jequoteform）组件 1.0b1 版本中存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。远程攻击者可向 index.php 的 view 参数传入包含「../」的恶意路径，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd）。该漏洞无需认证即可利用，攻击条件仅为目标部署了该缺陷组件且能访问前端页面，可能导致敏感信息泄露，并可能进一步造成其他未指定的严重影响。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2128"],"sources":["nuclei","cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2010-06-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该组件官方未发布修复版本，建议立即在 Joomla 后台禁用并卸载 JE Quotation Form（com_jequoteform）组件；若必须保留，应对 index.php 中 view 参数实施严格的路径白名单校验，过滤并拒绝包含「../」、空字节及绝对路径等目录遍历字符的输入，并升级 Joomla 核心至受支持的最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T17:14:00.476421223+00:00","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39832","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40187","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58593"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607"],"exp_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12607"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0093","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2122","title":"Joomla! Component simpledownload 0.9.5本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! com_simpledownload组件0.9.5版本存在目录穿越漏洞，攻击者可通过将controller参数设置为../遍历路径，读取任意本地文件如/etc/passwd。该漏洞源于未充分验证的用户输入允许访问不受限制的文件系统路径。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2122"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2010-06-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级Joomla! Component simpledownload至0.9.6或更高版本，启用path traversal防护，使用白名单文件访问机制验证用户输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T17:09:48.192371457+00:00","references":["http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/directory-a-documentation/downloads/10717","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlasimpledownload-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39871"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0082","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0082.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1982","title":"Joomla! JA Voice 组件 目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JA Voice（com_javoice）组件 2.0 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 index.php 的 view 参数时未对用户输入做充分过滤与路径规范化，远程攻击者可在 view 参数中构造包含“../”（点号点号）的恶意路径，跨越目录限制读取 Web 服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、口令文件等敏感内容）。该漏洞影响所有安装并启用 JA Voice 2.0 组件的 Joomla! 站点，无需身份认证，攻击者仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用，可导致敏感信息泄露，为进一步的系统入侵提供条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1982"],"sources":["cve","nvd","exploit-db","secunia"],"published":"2010-05-19","updated":"2010-05-19","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! JA Voice 2.0 组件；若业务必须保留，请升级至官方修复版本（移除或修复 com_javoice 中对 view 参数的处理，增加路径遍历过滤与白名单校验）；在过渡期间可通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）拦截包含 ../ 等目录遍历序列的 view 参数请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajavoice-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39202","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12121","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39343","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12121","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1982.yaml"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12121","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajavoice-lfi.txt"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0082.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0079","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1979","title":"Joomla! Affiliate Datafeeds 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Affiliate Datafeeds（com_datafeeds）组件 build 880 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 index.php 页面的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分的路径过滤与规范化，攻击者可构造包含 `..` 的路径穿越序列。由于该漏洞可被未经身份验证的远程攻击者利用，攻击条件仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求，影响范围涵盖所有运行该组件 build 880 的 Joomla! 站点。成功利用后，攻击者可读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、源代码及敏感系统文件，进而导致信息泄露与进一步的权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1979"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2010-05-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级 Affiliate Datafeeds（com_datafeeds）组件到官方发布的修复版本，或直接在 Joomla! 后台禁用或卸载该组件；若业务必须保留，应移除其对外暴露的访问入口。临时缓解措施：在网站根目录的 .htaccess 中添加规则，拦截向 index.php 的 controller 参数中包含 `..` 或路径穿越字符的请求，并通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）过滤目录遍历载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39360","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12088","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39246","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57570"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12088"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0077","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1957","title":"Joomla! Love Factory 组件 1.3.4 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Love Factory（com_lovefactory）组件 1.3.4 版本存在目录遍历导致的本地文件包含漏洞。该漏洞源于组件未对 index.php 的 controller 参数进行充分的路径校验，远程攻击者可在该参数中插入 ../ 序列，从而读取目标服务器上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd）。攻击无需身份认证，只需发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可被用于窃取敏感配置文件、应用源码及系统凭据，造成严重的信息泄露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1957"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Joomla! Love Factory 组件到厂商发布的最新安全版本，或直接卸载不再需要的组件；在文件包含逻辑中严格使用 basename() 等函数校验并规范化用户输入的路径，过滤 ../ 等目录遍历字符；对所有控制器参数进行白名单校验与 URL 编码处理；以最小权限运行 Web 服务进程，避免以 root 身份运行；在 Web 服务器层配置规则拦截常见的目录遍历请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/63803","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlalovefactory-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39471","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12235","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39512","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57849","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12235","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1957.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1957.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1957.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1957.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-1957-1863.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1957-1861.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1957_45.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-1957.yaml","https://github.com/wpsec/ARL-Source-Install/blob/aecf83f1f55a6f1a1a67dbe25e22ea0eb5a44bf2/tools/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1957.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1957_4.yaml"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12235"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12235"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0077.toml"}]